 The muffled sounds of the fighting outside could still reach me, but otherwise,
 I was completely alone inside the gateway's building.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Surrounded by luxury that itched to be carried away to a getaway car, I
 followed the main hallway towards a faint, blue shimmering light.
 Past an archway with all sorts of apocryphal inscriptions carved in a gold
