 keen on voicing her personal opinions, which could be easily discerned
 from the fact that I could see her through the glass pane, pouring actual
 dirt from a pot plant into the coffee machine.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
I returned to the briefing report laying on my desk, which contained little
 noteworthy intelligence on the Himalayan incident a few weeks before.
 There were some dark points to cover, but there were capable people on
 it, and I was pretty adamant that they'd get to the bottom of who was behind
 the resurgence of ghost yetis and bone dragons near McLeod Ganj.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
I had been singing paper after paper concerning logistics supplies, administrati
